'''停止資助警隊'''（{{lang-en|Defund the Police}}）是一个社會運動的口号，示威者希望政府減少或停止對警察部門的資助，并将其資源重新分配给非治安形式的[[公共安全|公共安全]]和社區服務上，例如社会服务，青年服务，住房，教育，医疗保健和其他社区资源。 

支持减少警察部门资金的社會活动家常常认为，对社区计划的投资可以为社区提供更好的威慑力；资金将直接用于解决[[社会问题|社会问题]]，例如如[[貧窮|贫困]]、[[露宿者|无家可归]]和[[精神疾患|精神错乱]]等等<ref name=":02">{{Cite web|title=What does 'defund the police' mean? The rallying cry sweeping the U要S – explained|url=http://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2020/jun/05/defunding-the-police-us-what-does-it-mean|accessdate=June 8, 2020|date=June 6, 2020|work=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120173134/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2020/jun/05/defunding-the-police-us-what-does-it-mean|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref name=":13">{{Cite web|title=What Exactly Does It Mean to Defund the Police?|url=https://www.thecut.com/2020/06/what-does-defund-the-police-mean-the-phrase-explained.html|accessdate=2020-06-16|author=Arnold|date=2020-06-12|first=Amanda|work=The Cut|language=en-us|archive-date=2020-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200623144937/https://www.thecut.com/2020/06/what-does-defund-the-police-mean-the-phrase-explained.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[廢警運動|廢除警隊主義者]]呼吁用其他[[公共安全|公共安全]]系统代替现有的[[警隊|警察]]部队，例如住房、就业、[[社區衛生|社区卫生]]、教育和其他计划<ref name=":12">{{Cite journal|title='Disband, Disempower, and Disarm': Amplifying the Theory and Practice of Police Abolition|last=McDowell|first=Meghan G.|last2=Fernandez|first2=Luis A.|date=July 20, 2018|journal=Critical Criminology|issue=3|doi=10.1007/s10612-018-9400-4|volume=26|pages=373–391}}</ref> <ref name=":17">{{Cite web|title=Towards the horizon of abolition: A conversation with Mariame Kaba|url=https://thenextsystem.org/learn/stories/towards-horizon-abolition-conversation-mariame-kaba|accessdate=|author=Kaba|date=November 9, 2017|first=Mariame|work=The Next System Project|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200621142632/https://thenextsystem.org/learn/stories/towards-horizon-abolition-conversation-mariame-kaba|archivedate=2020-06-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

